2. Description of Service

MorseGenie is a lightweight utility bot for Zoho Cliq that:

Converts English text to Morse code

Converts Morse code to English

Provides simple help commands and quick responses

The bot is provided as-is, with no guarantee of accuracy beyond reasonable effort.

